************* Theory **************
version control system is software helps software development teams to manage changes to source code over time.

it keeps track of every modification to source code in special kind of database. 

types-->
1. central--> ek central repository aste..tithun developer source code ghetat and then commit back to central.
2. distributed--> every user la local repository aste...jith te modify karu shaktat and later they push it to central.

why we need?
rollback
backup
bug tracking
collaboration
limited undo ations..to platforms like neatbeans ecllipse

